HEADWORD: G-Jo
<hw>G-Jo</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A Chinese and Japanese medical
treatment of symptoms by applying pressure with the fingers to specific
pressure points on the body.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> acupressure, shiatsu.</syn>⟦br⟧
